|                |   [6x6] * [6x1]   |    123 ns |    126 ns |    120 ns |    130 ns |      97 ns |      88 ns |          91 ns |
|                |  [200x6] * [6x1]  |    781 ns |    982 ns |  1.065 us |  1.943 us |   1.172 us |   1.203 us |       1.171 us |
