The previous table shows the following trend:
- MKL sounds the fastest third-party if you want to speed up basic linear algebra in ViSP
- OpenBLAS, Netlib and Atlas have similar intermediate performance results
- GSL, lapack built-in and operations performed without lapack are the slowest with similar results.
 
